title: Southern Pines Animal Shelter

review.description: They're great with their animals. They work hard to promote them and get them adopted. I've even adopted two cats from them. I highly recommend them to anyone interested in adopting an animal.
My husband and I adopted our sweet Nova from Southern Pines. Our adoption experience was great. Very helpful and friendly staff. We wouldn't trade our pup for the world. Thank you, Southern Pines!
